           then
           do
             string1 = 'Not enough space on drive '||ppath||' to hold the '||Ctl.!ProgName||' files.'
             string2 = Ctl.!ProgName 'requires' space_required 'bytes of free space.'
             say '旼컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴컴커'
